KNOW THYSELF<br/>
For those ready to begin, progress, return to, remember or advance up the path of High Magic, we offer our lantern to guide you to the threshold of your own interior temple. From there, it is up to you to dive into the self, the process, the magic as far as you are willing to go. Our Lodge is self-Initiatory. Our school is hidden but to those with eyes to see. When the student is ready, the teacher appears.<br/>
